52ef0a171","tid":2065620,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"我想問PGDE practicum 係點做? 去中學搵?? 定係點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:55:00.000Z","msg":"Full time 係院校幫你搵， PT 係你已經做緊果間度實習返。"},{"pid":"2a475f643dd9f5a597fade3614b5e482bf7b3cee","tid":2065620,"uid":191145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fc9c9dec3dd7919987f4b59166803dcf317641b","tid":2065620,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a83c47934cf394bcc45f4f0977119ed41970215","tid":2065620,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b31f2c246fa4c7fc7c69d5d664ea44f372757b5","tid":2065620,"uid":131622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:51:35.000Z","msg":"搵你現職學校幫手，冇就由pgde院校安排俾你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:54:35.000Z","msg":"如果係secondary level , 安排個啲係中學?要full time 教幾耐？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"仲有如果我冇英文基準試... 我可唔可以去中學做Practicum 教英文?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:02:05.000Z","msg":"你知唔知自己讀左咩PGDE架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報英文去實習咪英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n實習6-8星期x2次<br />\n<br />\n基準還基準 到你搵工係兩個requirement 黎<br />\nEng Degree+PGDE+LPAT係一個package 黎<br />\n前兩個一定要有 最尾個樣可以靠佢地豁免"}]}